
This list is still outdated.
Please report your experience and additions.

Mac OS X, MacPorts:
  port install ruby
  port install mysql5
  port install mysql5-devel
  port install rb-rubygems
  port install rb-dbi +dbd_mysql
  port install ImageMagick

Linux Packages, Ubuntu/Debian:
  apt-get install ruby1.8
  apt-get install rubygems
  apt-get install build-essentials
  apt-get install mysql-server-5.0
  apt-get install imagemagick
  apt-get install libdbd-mysql-ruby
  apt-get install libmagick9-dev

Rubygems (select newest version available):
  gem install mysql
  gem install rack
  gem install highline
  gem install eventmachine
  gem install daemons
  gem install httpclient
  gem install thin
  gem install mkmf
  gem install soap4r
  gem install rmagick
  gem install json

Locally, execute:
  pushd
  cd lib/util/randgen_c
  ruby extconf.rb
  popd

